3. Design Goals

Lights (traditional, automatic)
Door Locks (mechanical, electro-magnetic, garage door)
Faucets
Heating/Cooling (thermostat, thermal sensors)
Security (camera, motion sensing)
Contextual Mobility Services (geographical based triggers)
Car Interface/UI
Smart-Mirror

